{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji30.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给陈文新的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给陈文新的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1951年4月29日）文新同志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的信和你母亲的信都收到了，很高兴。希望你们姊妹们努力学习或工作，继承你父亲的遗志，为人民国家的建设服务。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问候你的母亲。祝进步！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四月二十九日[1]陈文新，当时是武汉大学农学院的学生。[2]即陈昌，新民学会会员，中国共产党的早期党员，1930年牺牲。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1951,"month":4,"day":29}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":264,"page_end":264},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}